title: Two Storied House for Sale in Katubedda
details: Two Storied house available for Sale in Katubedda, Moratuwa, built on a 9 Perches land. The house consists of all the facilities required for comfortable living. Consists 4 Bedrooms, 2 Attached Bathroom, Common Bathroom, Washroom, Living room, Dining room, Pantry, Mini Library, Servant Room & Bathroom.
